CHAPTER 2 â€“ Evolution of SharePoint (History)

1990s

Started as a web-based document management system.


2001 â€“ SharePoint Portal Server

First official release.


2007 â€“ SharePoint MOSS

Big jump with workflows, metadata, enterprise search.


2010 â€“ SharePoint Server 2010

Sandbox solutions, BCS, improved UI.


2013 â€“ SharePoint Server 2013

Modern apps, cloud-first direction.


2016 â€“ Hybrid SharePoint

Integration with Microsoft 365.


2019 â€“ Last On-Prem Modern Version

Modern UI, hybrid support.


