âœ” Site Name & URL

âœ” Site Template (Modern only)

âœ” Site Owners

âœ” Storage Quota

âœ” Sharing Level

Anyone with link

New and existing guests

Only existing guests

Only internal users


âœ” Sensitivity Labels

Control classification:

Public

Confidential

Highly Confidential


âœ” Delete or Restore Site

Deleted sites go to Site Recycle Bin (93 days retention)



