8.5 Sharing Settings (Tenant-Level)

Controls who can share and how.

Sharing Levels (Most restrictive â†’ Least restrictive)

1. Only people in your organization


2. Specific people


3. People with existing access


4. Anyone with the link (Anonymous)



Control per site:

Example:
HR site â†’ Only internal sharing
Project site â†’ Anyone sharing allowed


---

8.6 Access Control (Security Core)

Controls:

1. Unmanaged Device Access

Allow full access

