8.25 Real-Time Admin Scenarios

Scenario 1: Employee left company

Admin must:

Access userâ€™s OneDrive

Transfer files to manager

Reassign ownership in SharePoint

Disable sign-in

Retention policies keep files safe



---

Scenario 2: User unable to sync files

Steps:

Check OneDrive sync logs

Check file name restrictions

Check network restrictions

Reset sync client



---

Scenario 3: Too much storage usage

Admin can:

Increase quota

Move sites

Archive old content

Apply retention



---

Scenario 4: Sensitive files leaked

Admin should:

Check audit logs

Apply DLP

Lock site

Revoke sharing links



